      <title>纽约市长被起诉。飓风海伦预计将造成灾难性后果</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/09/26/g-s1-24634/up-first-newsletter-new-york-city-mayor-eric-adams-indictment-hurricane-helene</link>
